<%- include('./partials/header') %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/about.css">

<!-- Hero Section -->
<div class="about-hero">
  <h1 class="about-hero-title">About TorqueX</h1>
  <p class="about-hero-subtitle">Driving Innovation in Premium Car Rentals</p>
</div>

<div class="about-container">
  <div class="about-layout">
    <!-- Left Column -->
    <div>
      <!-- Feature Image -->
      <div class="about-feature-image">
        <img 
          src="https://www.shutterstock.com/image-photo/vertical-photo-headlight-modern-prestigious-600nw-1947016213.jpg" 
          alt="Luxury vehicle fleet" 
          onerror="this.src='/images/placeholder.jpg'; this.onerror=null;"
        >
        <div class="about-image-overlay"></div>
        <p class="about-image-caption">Premium Fleet Experience</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Mission Card -->
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-header">
          <svg class="about-card-icon blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
          <h2 class="about-card-title">Our Mission</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          At TorqueX, our mission is to provide exceptional vehicle rental experiences that exceed our customers' expectations. We believe in offering premium vehicles at competitive prices, backed by outstanding customer service.
        </p>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          We strive to make the rental process as seamless as possible, from browsing our selection to returning your vehicle, ensuring your journey is as enjoyable as your destination.
        </p>
        <div class="about-quote">
          <p class="about-quote-text">
            "Your journey begins with the perfect ride"
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column -->
    <div>
      <!-- Our Story -->
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-header">
          <svg class="about-card-icon green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
          </svg>
          <h2 class="about-card-title">Our Story</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          Founded with a clear vision to redefine convenience and reliability, TorqueX has always stood at the intersection of innovation and customer-centric service. Our mission has been simple: to make premium mobility accessible, transparent, and technologically advanced.
        </p>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          From the very beginning, we invested in smart systems, digital bookings, and modern fleet management tools that allowed us to deliver a seamless rental experience. What started as a modest venture with limited resources quickly transformed into a technology-driven mobility platform trusted by individuals, families, and businesses.
        </p>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          As mobility evolved, so did we. TorqueX expanded its services to include long-term rentals, corporate leasing solutions, and customizable travel packagesâ€”ensuring that every customer finds exactly what they need, when they need it.
        </p>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          Empower every journey with comfort, confidence, and cutting-edge technology.
        </p>
        
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="about-stat-card">
            <div class="about-stat-number blue">500+</div>
            <div class="about-stat-label">Vehicles</div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat-card">
            <div class="about-stat-number green">10K+</div>
            <div class="about-stat-label">Happy Customers</div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat-card">
            <div class="about-stat-number purple">5</div>
            <div class="about-stat-label">Years Experience</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Why Choose TorqueX -->
      <div class="about-card" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
        <div class="about-card-header">
          <svg class="about-card-icon yellow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z"></path>
          </svg>
          <h2 class="about-card-title">Why Choose TorqueX?</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="about-features-list">
          <li class="about-feature-item">
            <svg class="about-feature-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="about-feature-text">Premium vehicles at competitive prices</span>
          </li>
          <li class="about-feature-item">
            <svg class="about-feature-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="about-feature-text">Flexible rental periods with no hidden fees</span>
          </li>
          <li class="about-feature-item">
            <svg class="about-feature-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="about-feature-text">24/7 customer support</span>
          </li>
          <li class="about-feature-item">
            <svg class="about-feature-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="about-feature-text">Convenient pickup and drop-off locations</span>
          </li>
          <li class="about-feature-item">
            <svg class="about-feature-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="about-feature-text">Regular maintenance and safety checks on all vehicles</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Meet Our Team -->
  <div class="about-team-section">
    <h2 class="about-team-title">Meet Our Team</h2>
    <div class="about-team-grid">
      
      <!-- Team Member 1 -->
      <div class="about-team-card">
        <div class="about-team-avatar blue">
